{"tid":1838242,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「港殤之柱」矗立丹麥國會外","createTime":"2020-01-24T02:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T04:00:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":141,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"2771c97e1aea0e4c2a12b98705c5f48c8b9668af","tid":1838242,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T02:58:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200124/EYN6ODI6CZBUXOALEKOP7MGALA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200124%2FEYN6ODI6CZBUXOALEKOP7MGALA%2F&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JXwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=fb23ae3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200124%2FEYN6ODI6CZBUXOALEKOP7MGALA%2F&h=cf082484\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200124/EYN6ODI6CZBUXOALEKOP7MGALA/</a><br />\n<br />\n「港殤之柱」矗立丹麥國會外<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200124/large/1579799579_c36c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200124%2Flarge%2F1579799579_c36c.jpg&h=0bf06025&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n15人糾纏在一起的「羞恥之柱」，旁有配以黃色安全帽和面罩的示威者塑像。<br />\n(社內相)<br />\n<br />\n丹麥首都哥本哈根國會外昨日豎立起一個八米高、重約三噸的銅像「羞恥之柱」，刻劃出15人糾纏在一起的畫面，底座寫着「丹麥與香港站在一起」和「老一輩不能永遠殺害年輕一輩」，環繞銅像的柱上還掛有示威者頭部、配以黃色安全帽和面罩的塑像。製作的雕塑家表示，銅像代表丹麥人支持香港人爭取民主和言論自由。 <br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"a7ff540ccde6e95ee57487c48e5ef38e50f8c2ee","tid":1838242,"uid":70685,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:23:32.000Z","msg":"支柱真係講香港？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"395c338c0d5931b71b25e860271664f3420eaf50","tid":1838242,"uid":14449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:23:55.000Z","msg":"丹麥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgm